-- United Airlines says 787 fleet flying as scheduled
-- 
-- Wed Jan 16, 2013 3:58pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/01/16/us-boeing-787-united-idUSBRE90F11I20130116

 

 (Reuters) - United Continental Holdings Inc's United Airlines has inspected its fleet of Boeing Co 787 Dreamliners and all are flying as scheduled, the airline said on Wednesday. 
 Two of the largest 787 customers have grounded their Dreamliner fleets following the latest safety incident on Wednesday. (Reporting By  Ben Berkowitz ; Editing by Gerald E. McCormick)